## Only the symlinked Claude artifacts are tracked under claude/;
## auth (.credentials.json), history, and runtime state stay ignored
## by construction, even if something stray lands in the directory.
claude/*
!claude/commands
!claude/skills
!claude/scripts
!claude/CLAUDE.md
!claude/statusline.sh
!claude/settings.json

## converter caches
convert/**/__pycache__/
convert/tests/.pytest_cache/
